          "_name": "news04",
          "_sourceTheme": "startm5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"news04\" group=\"News\">\n  <mbr-parameters>\n    <header>Size</header>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\">\n    <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"10\">\n    <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"4\">\n    <input type=\"range\" name=\"textWidth\" title=\"Width\" min=\"4\" max=\"12\" value=\"11\" step=\"1\">\n    <header>Show/Hide</header>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showMainTitle\" checked>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Subtitle\" name=\"showMainSubtitle\">\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Event Name\" name=\"showTitle\">\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Date\" name=\"showSubtitle\">\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Buttons\" name=\"showButtons\">\n    <input type=\"color\" title=\"Card BG\" name=\"cardbg\" value=\"#49243e\" selected>\n    <header>Background</header>\n    <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" name=\"bgColor\" value=\"#49243e\">\n  </mbr-parameters>\n  <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n    <div class=\"col-12 mb-5 content-head\" mbr-if=\"showMainTitle || showMainSubtitle\">\n      <h3 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style align-center mb-0\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" mbr-if=\"showMainTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\"><b>Refund and Cancellation Policy</b></h3>\n      <h5 class=\"mbr-section-subtitle mbr-fonts-style align-center mb-0 mt-4\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showMainSubtitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-subtitle\">\n        Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit.\n      </h5>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"row justify-content-center \">\n      <div class=\" col-12 col-lg-{{textWidth}}\">\n        <div class=\"item features-without-image col-12 active\">\n          <div class=\"item-wrapper\">\n            <h5 class=\"mbr-card-title mbr-fonts-style mt-0 mb-3\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-card-title\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\">\n              <b>G</b></h5>\n            <h6 class=\"mbr-card-subtitle mbr-fonts-style mt-0 mb-3\" mbr-if=\"showSubtitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-card-subtitle\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\">\n              May 17-18, 2025\n            </h6>\n            <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style mt-0 mb-3\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text, .item .mbr-section-btn\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\">Last updated: April 17, 2025<br><br>At Bestie Talk, we aim to provide the best experience for our users. Please review our refund and cancellation policy below for more details regarding our approach:<br><br><b>No Standard Refund Policy</b><br>Our platform operates on a coin-based system, where customers purchase coins as needed to access services. We do not offer a standard refund or cancellation policy.<br><br><b>Refunds for Payment Failures</b><br>In the case of payment failures or issues during the transaction process, we thoroughly verify the problem and, if valid, refund the deducted amount to the customer’s account.<br><br><b>Coin Reversion for Technical Issues</b><br>If a technical issue causes coins to be deducted without the user receiving the intended service, we will investigate the matter and, if confirmed, reverse the coins to the customer’s account.<br><br><b>Refund Processing Time</b><br>If a refund is approved by Bestie Talk, the amount will be credited to the customer within 5-7 working days.<br><br><b>No Refund for Used Coins</b><br>Once coins are used for services, they cannot be refunded or canceled. We encourage users to ensure their coins are used for the desired services.<br><br><b>Case-by-Case Exception Handling</b><br>We handle any disputes or exceptional cases on an individual basis, ensuring fairness and customer satisfaction. If you experience any issues with the service, please contact our support team at <a href=\"mailto:NYM IT Solutionscustomerservice@gmail.com\" class=\"text-primary\">NYM IT Solutionscustomerservice@gmail.com</a> for assistance.<br></p>\n            <div mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" class=\"mbr-section-btn\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove\"><a class=\"btn btn-white\" href=\"https://mobiri.se\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">\n                Learn more</a></div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        \n        \n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>",
          "_cid": "uxid8ARepm",
          "_anchor": "news04-24",
